[Nouns] sage, wise man; master mind, master spirit of the age; longhead, thinker.
authority, oracle, luminary, shining light, esprit fort, magnus Apollo, Solon, Solomon, Nestor, Magi, "second Daniel."
man of learning [more]; expert [more]; wizard [more].
[Ironically] wiseacre, bigwig.
[Adjectives] venerable, reverenced, emeritus.
